article_metadata.description: Open-enrollment packets have reminded local employees in recent weeks that the U.S. health-care system is the most-expensive in the world. Employee-benefits consultant Aon Hewitt is forecasting a 6.9?percent increase in overall annual premium costs in the Columbus area next year, with the average total premium cost per local employee reaching $10,777.
